<h2 class="bold font-l">Ghostbusters (1984)</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Dana Barrett opens her refrigerator to see a portal to another dimension guarded by the Terror Dog Zuul, which growls out its own name to her revealing a bright light from its mouth. </p>
</div>
